    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is paired with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox, providing direct mechanical engagement. The chassis benefits from a functional Variable M Differential Lock and recent inspection of the rear subframe mounting points. The VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal cam timing, and the valve clearances were recently shimmed to factory specifications. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with a 'good' classification, the performance envelope remains intact, offering precise turn-in via the 15.4:1 steering rack and consistent stopping power from the ventilated rotors. A mechanically sound driver\u2019s car for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
