    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered for your consideration is a 2019 Executive Sport Sedan that perfectly captures the essence of refined performance. This vehicle has been driven with care and serves as a testament to diligent ownership. The exterior is finished in a timeless Metallic Charcoal that holds a deep, reflective shine, showing only the inevitable minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the passenger door. \n\nInside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort. The black Nappa leather seats are firm and supportive, exhibiting only light bolster wear on the driver's side, while the walnut wood trim and brushed aluminum accents are free of cracks or fading. Every amenity, including the dual-zone climate control, heated steering wheel, and the 12-speaker premium audio system, operates flawlessly. \n\nMechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with a comprehensive log of oil changes, fluid flushes, and filter replacements. The turbocharged engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the all-wheel-drive system provides confident handling in all weather conditions. Recent maintenance includes a brand-new set of performance tires and a fresh brake service. This is a turnkey luxury vehicle that offers a sophisticated driving experience without the 'new car' price tag. Included are two key fobs, the original owner's manuals, and a clean vehicle history report.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
