    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically robust example of the high-revving S54 platform. It features the sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS rebuild and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate common chassis fatigue. The 3.2L atmospheric inline-six pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from six individual throttle bodies that offer exceptional transient throttle response. While the finish shows minor honest wear reflective of its 'good' status, the drivetrain remains tight and the suspension geometry is dialed for the purist. A turn-key, driver-grade icon ready for the canyons.",
